WeldEstimator - Clojure application for estimating time & materials for welding
===============================================================================

What you'll need to build WeldEstimator
---------------------------------------

 * Git  http://git-scm.com/download
 * Apache Ant  http://ant.apache.org/bindownload.cgi
 * JDK (version 1.5 or later)  http://java.sun.com/javase/downloads/index.jsp

How to build WeldEstimator
--------------------------

 * Use git to clone the repository:  git clone git://github.com/barryteel/weld-estimator.git
 * Move into the weld-estimator directory:  cd weld-estimator
 * Use Ant to compile the source code and launch the application:  ant
